extends local.server.Proxy
implements org.zoolu.sip.transaction.TransactionClientListener, TestNATListener

Class SessionBorderController implements a Session Border Controller SIP Server.
The SBC check if a peer is behind NAT and assigns the public address to local peer.

Author:
Fabrizio Caramia
